        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/community-reporting-tips-idaho-schools">
                                    We Enlisted a Community to Help Us Report on One State’s Crumbling Schools. Here’s How You Can Do the Same.
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Do you want to document problems with school facilities around your state? Reporters from ProPublica and The Idaho Statesman offer some tips.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/asia-fields">Asia Fields</a>, ProPublica,  with <span class="name">Becca Savransky</span>, <a href="https://www.idahostatesman.com/">Idaho Statesman</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-10-01EDT05:00">Oct. 1, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
